I still can't do it at all.

00:06:44.020 --> 00:06:46.400
If you want, I can give you some pointers.

00:06:46.400 --> 00:06:49.610
Huh?! You know how to play, Kazama-<i>san</i>?

00:06:49.610 --> 00:06:52.780
Well, yeah, I used to play.

00:07:06.460 --> 00:07:08.340
It didn't even touch the rim...

00:07:08.340 --> 00:07:10.090
Yeah, it sure feels nice.

00:07:10.090 --> 00:07:14.600
Just try to throw the ball high,
and that should help... I think.

00:07:14.600 --> 00:07:16.350
