00:07:37.950 --> 00:07:40.910
Oh, a <i>senpai </i>told me the same thing.

00:07:42.540 --> 00:07:44.290
I can do this.

00:07:47.630 --> 00:07:49.050
Here goes!

00:07:51.260 --> 00:07:52.550
Kazama-<i>kun</i>.

00:07:52.550 --> 00:07:55.930
