some rice balls or something.

00:08:12.950 --> 00:08:15.320
I could eat a ton of those.

00:08:15.320 --> 00:08:16.990
--All right, then.
--Yeah.

00:08:24.870 --> 00:08:26.840
Let's grab a bite to eat before we leave.

00:08:26.840 --> 00:08:30.090
Okay, how about the pizza place
in front of the station?

00:08:30.090 --> 00:08:32.050
Oh, sounds good!

00:08:33.590 --> 00:08:35.260
Hey, Tsukishiro!

00:08:35.260 --> 00:08:36.510
