00:10:15.320 --> 00:10:18.950
Hey, that's totally fine. They look
cuter when they're round.

00:10:18.950 --> 00:10:19.860
Really?

00:10:19.860 --> 00:10:20.950
Yeah.

00:10:23.280 --> 00:10:27.290
