sucked into the palm of your hand.

00:10:27.290 --> 00:10:28.540
Okay.

00:10:30.750 --> 00:10:34.840
Hey, guys! Want to break for lunch soon?

00:10:36.460 --> 00:10:38.680
Let's eat!

00:10:40.550 --> 00:10:41.510
This is <i>so </i>good.

00:10:41.510 --> 00:10:44.100
I'm glad. Eat as many as you want.

00:10:44.100 --> 00:10:46.850
Thank you so much for teaching me today.

00:10:46.850 --> 00:10:51.190
I wanted the exercise, too,
so it's no problem at all.

00:10:51.190 --> 00:10:52.230
It's just...

00:10:52.230 --> 00:10:53.270
