Sakurai-<i>san </i>are here, too!

00:11:21.930 --> 00:11:25.430
Yeah, they're both here.

00:11:25.430 --> 00:11:27.850
Hey, what are you guys doing here?

00:11:27.850 --> 00:11:29.560
