00:11:31.690 --> 00:11:34.310
Thank you so much!

00:11:34.310 --> 00:11:36.820
Basketball! That brings back memories.

00:11:36.820 --> 00:11:39.650
Takeda-<i>san</i>, you look like you could dunk.

00:11:39.650 --> 00:11:42.660
Everyone, thank you for coming today!

00:11:42.660 --> 00:11:45.490
It's our pleasure. Let's do this!

00:11:45.490 --> 00:11:48.160
Yeah!

